Ok, before we start, let me ask you first if you have already know how to install/download Laravel, since installing Laravel is another topic, you can go in this <a title="How to install Laravel on WAMP for beginners" href="http://www.darwinbiler.com/how-to-install-laravel-on-wamp-for-beginners/" target="_blank">page</a>first then go back here and we will kick some ass.

